title: Zizzi's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of Italian restaurant chain, this one is at the top of the High St. Has high ceiling and open plan kitchen. Vegans could have olives starter; the primavera with vegan cheese; roasted aubergine, artichokes, peppers; and a slow roasted tomatoes, olives & fresh oregano, served with a slaw. Has vegan cheese. Two of the pasta dishes can be altered to be vegan. For dessert there are fruit sorbets.
